{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2960909, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有同学能在一分钟之内想出解法吗……我是不行，想了差不多五分钟", "timestamp": 1637098182, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960914, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "1/4？", "timestamp": 1637098976, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或许试试递推数列？", "timestamp": 1637105063, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960972, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "试试鞅论，停时过程", "timestamp": 1637105784, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960993, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "按每个数字第一次出现的位置算，无非就是2，4，6全部出现在1，3，5之前，而六个数字对称，所以答案是 允许的排列数3！*3！除以总排列数6！等于1/20", "timestamp": 1637106781, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2960998, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "也就是说每个数字第一次出现的顺序有一个排列 比如 216435，每种排列的地位等同所以概率等同，那么就找所有满足条件的排列有多少就行了", "timestamp": 1637106902, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2960998, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是出现所有偶数的意思不是只出现一次吧？比如2246135 也符合题意吧", "timestamp": 1637107234, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961015, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961014, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 就按每个数字第一次出现的位置的先后组成一个排列", "timestamp": 1637107278, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961014, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 1，3，5第一次出现的位置全部排在2，4，6第一次出现的位置之后，完全就是题目要求", "timestamp": 1637107334, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961020, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961014, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 出现了几次完全不管。", "timestamp": 1637107351, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961022, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961014, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 按第一次出现的位置作为特征，这个特征对不同的数字也是对称的", "timestamp": 1637107403, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2960998, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不对，因为一旦扔到一个奇数就终止了，你的sample space不对", "timestamp": 1637107448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961026, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961023, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 假设无限扔下去有什么问题呢？反正判定条件一样，后面扔或者不扔不影响结果，我就要继续扔", "timestamp": 1637107506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961028, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961023, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 题目本身也没说停止吧", "timestamp": 1637107542, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961029, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "50%", "timestamp": 1637107546, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961033, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961023, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 在第一个奇数前出现所有偶数 等于 在所有奇数前出现所有偶数 等于 所有偶数第一次出现的位置均早于所有奇数第一次出现的位置", "timestamp": 1637107660, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961093, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961033, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我写了一个蒙特卡洛模拟程序，发现还就是0.05😯", "timestamp": 1637109168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961033, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 重复100000000次实验，确实是0.05", "timestamp": 1637109209, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961033, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 有道理", "timestamp": 1637109271, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961033, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 或许最初的想法有某些隐含的道理，不过我认为p(n)其中n为总共投掷次数（前n-1次的偶数和最后一次为奇数且前面所有偶数包含246）收敛到1/20，才是正确的一个path", "timestamp": 1637109820, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961184, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961147, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 将暴力求和视为正确path是在侮辱数学", "timestamp": 1637110310, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2961191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第一想法是马氏链，状态包括 初始，见过一个偶数，见过两个偶数，见过三个偶数，见到奇数(终止)\n不过好像没上面的方法好", "timestamp": 1637110476, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2964075, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2960972, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 展开讲讲", "timestamp": 1637134181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2971032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 561852, "reply_to": 2961184, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 凭直觉没有严谨的证明才是在侮辱数学", "timestamp": 1637204652, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 16, "pid": 561852, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "求投一个骰子在第一个奇数前出现所有偶数的概率", "timestamp": 1637098115, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637204652, "url": "", "vote": {}}}